OL,3,CFirework display marks 50 years since
OL,4,Copening of iconic Swindon leisure
OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FCredit: Dronie Productions
OL,9,FA spectacular firework display has
OL,10,Fmarked 50 years since the opening of
OL,11,FSwindon's Oasis Leisure Centre.
OL,13,FThe iconic centre opened it's doors on
OL,14,Fthe 1 January 1976 and operated as a
OL,15,Fmulti-purpose venue before it closed
OL,16,Fin November 2020.
OL,18,FThe Grade II listed leisure centre was
OL,19,Fknown for its domed roof and lagoon
OL,20,Fswimming pool which included a wave
OL,21,Fmachine and multiple slides.
