OL,7,FIt also had sports facilities and an
OL,8,Fevents space which hosted concerts by
OL,9,Fmusic stars including Ed Sheeran and
OL,10,FKings of Leon.
OL,12,FHowever in November 2020, following
OL,13,FCOVID-19 lockdowns, the centre closed
OL,14,Fafter operator GLL surrendered their
OL,15,Flease of the building saying it was no
OL,16,Flonger "viable" to run because of the
OL,17,Ffinancial impact of the pandemic.
