OL,7,FA local action group called 'Save
OL,8,FOasis Swindon' has campaigned for the
OL,9,Freopening of the leisure centre since
OL,10,F2021.
OL,12,FThis year they raised more than #6,000
OL,13,Fto hold the firework display to
OL,14,Fcelebrate the centre's 50th birthday.
OL,16,FOrganiser and campaigner creator Neil
OL,17,FRobinson described the event as
OL,18,F'absolutely amazing'.
