OL,7,F"The turnout exceeded my expectations,
OL,8,FI didn't expect that many people to
OL,9,Fturn up.
OL,11,F"It was a really big community effort.
OL,12,FWe had Ivo Graham, the comedian, come
OL,13,Fdown to help us with the countdown as
OL,14,Fwell. It just flowed together
OL,15,Fbeautifully."
OL,17,FWhen asked what inspired him to set up
OL,18,Fthe campaign group, he said: "The
OL,19,FOasis is so iconic, I grew up with it.
