OL,7,F"I learnt to swim there as a kid and I
OL,8,Ftook my daughter there just before it
OL,9,Fshut during Covid.
OL,11,F"I was very sad when it closed because
OL,12,FI wanted my daughter to do swimming
OL,13,Flessons there - that's why I set the
OL,14,Fwhole campaign up."
OL,16,FWhat's next for Oasis Leisure Centre?
OL,18,FIn 2023 leaseholders Seven Capital and
OL,19,Flandowners Swindon Borough Council
OL,20,Fsaid they hoped to reopen the centre
OL,21,Fin time for its 50th anniversary.
