OL,5,Ccentre
OL,7,FIn July 2025 Seven Capital, a property
OL,8,Fdevelopment company, received planning
OL,9,Fpermission to refurbish Oasis with the
OL,10,Flisted pool area and dome retained but
OL,11,Fthe sports hall demolished.
OL,13,FHowever, their proposal to build more
OL,14,Fthan 700 flats on the site was
OL,15,Frejected.
OL,17,FThe company, who say the housing was
OL,18,Fvital to fund the restoration,
OL,19,Fdescribed the decision as a "major
OL,20,Fblow" to the leisure centre's future.
